{"tid":1896122,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"狗鐵都同你玩攬炒，因應疫情減少班次 等乘客盡量填滿車箱","createTime":"2020-02-25T03:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T03:22:57.000Z","uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2a2f7f33ced8fcf6d13e16639846da05b4a5f11c","tid":1896122,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/mtr-19_sWfMM_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fmtr-19_sWfMM_1200x0.png&h=b745ec2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，因應最近新型冠狀病毒病疫情，令乘客量顯著下跌，二月首兩週乘客量急跌五成。所以由本周六起，將暫時調整多條鐵路綫的非繁忙時段列車服務，非繁忙時段會維持平均每 3-8 分鐘一班車，乘客在非繁忙時段候車時間平均會延長半分鐘至約兩分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69470d3dd823ae32fc434248d9b9f10287b6a9f6","tid":1896122,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:14:21.000Z","msg":"立場係咪食開最新嘅毒品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7ec8cd45983fe3adca94646a5cb0cb0b0d9380","tid":1896122,"uid":320902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:22:57.000Z","msg":"呢排好多人插立場"}]}